title: O'Neill - SUPERKINI ONE WAY RUNWAY
description:
Between April 1st and May 15th the search is on to find the new O'Neill Girl

But it's not just any girl who will make the cut -- it's a girl who has the guts to jump off the end of the One Way Runway and into the sea wearing the new O'Neill Superkini.

Twelve finalists from the O'Neill Girls Facebook campaign will be flown out to Ibiza in June to walk the One Way Runway in front of a panel of judges to include supermodel Elyse Taylor, professional O'Neill surfer Malia Manuel, Raine Jackson and top fashion editors and stylists.
